    "body": "There's some documentation on the `run_tests.py` script, but you do have to know where to find it - https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/tools/run_tests/README.md\r\n\r\nI'm not sure it makes sense to adapt the `make test` target, since there's other ways of running the tests that we naturally spend effort maintaining for our pull request tests, etc."
